</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="205E9D66EAB86F112E595B8D0E9E3531" pageId="null" pageNumber="363" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="4AF2CF43BCC3813C100522E36A67DE18" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Zusammengezogene Trespe</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="1B8AE0F199F46ADC7F51F00DCBF1ED7C" pageId="null" pageNumber="363" type="description">
<paragraph id="85398DE99A6A6A5EA28D441DB3CA6054" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="EAED95CD4B62EA8B6D3AF0163E2AE76A" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Bromus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="363" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="erectus">
<emphasis id="6E084324770C90AEAAA5059A8028665A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">B. erectus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<normalizedToken id="A91350CBEBB6E7887B7A3986B04AD259" originalValue="Grundständige" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Grundstaendige</normalizedToken>
Scheiden faserig verwitternd; an der ganzen Pflanze keine steife Behaarung: 
<emphasis id="6410A03666A9CB040055EACACC8FA1CB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
<normalizedToken id="530194E21C8C84EA62A44600D93C4DFE" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oberseits flaumig behaart oder kahl, am Rande nie mit abstehenden, steifen Haaren.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="9A9F539616339EEA8C57CC752520809E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="AA5D9661BE1ECAC8A631DBBB391566B3" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="F62A406A8828E58DE3C4B0F539DA4B34" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="3D935EFA920C06FB3B5FC96C8CAE0B90" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5943CF6778CDC2A86776701D803630AF" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
<emphasis id="FAE853B6643A3C7AF653BE5F948E7748" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="67107A1C76F1767C3C1A53BDBEA25A94" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
<emphasis id="F3845DCB66C44A2BB2628FADAC26C4C3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Kalkhaltige bis saure 
<normalizedToken id="0028F194FE4AD3C5AFF925CA9EC660A6" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Boeden</normalizedToken>
; steile, nur 
<normalizedToken id="3370375BAE02B23A6A947B9AEE682885" originalValue="südexponierte" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">suedexponierte</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="FEED8168206462B6E3765D2FA3A2B60D" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Haenge</normalizedToken>
in Gebieten mit insubrischem Klima (bis 200 cm Niederschlag). Trockene Wiesen, 
<normalizedToken id="D3879D0DF9A42AFCB75D3C12E4AC87D0" originalValue="Felshänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Felshaenge</normalizedToken>
; oft im 
<emphasis id="F858902C892779F9C93A5A412080E8BE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
Andropogonetum 
<taxonomicName id="AA59659537DB624D6683F94EFCEA6693" authority="W. Koch 1943" authorityName="W. Koch" authorityYear="1943" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Grylli" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="363" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insubricum">Grylli insubricum W. Koch 1943</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
. 
<normalizedToken id="06355E4AEBEED6B2D31EE3CD0DB6CC28" originalValue="Ausführliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Ausfuehrliche</normalizedToken>
Angaben 
<normalizedToken id="4108C01A6FA19C7722426DA044486516" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">ueber</normalizedToken>
Standort und Soziologie von Koch (1943a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DFDB643326307C86E0C055DCD841E825" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
<emphasis id="F1151A7FFF08179B5C98CB582301C66C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="C64EF104A4C4E6A944CD330A8931C52B" originalValue="Südalpen-Pflanze" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Suedalpen-Pflanze</normalizedToken>
:
</emphasis>
Vom 
<normalizedToken id="501D70945AAC5C9DF3D135DA1699B8AD" originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Tessin (Verbreitung dort wahrscheinlich wie 
<taxonomicName id="08E0EA82D8B3D2EBF608098AE1ECEECC" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Chrysopogon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="363" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gryllus">
<emphasis id="4E940529BB2AE69A453DDED0A76457EB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">Chrysopogon Gryllus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) 
<normalizedToken id="273BCF80C8A02FCB40F9DCCE4A3DC56A" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="363">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Istrien, Kroatien und Albanien. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1964).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
